#: ../../docs/classes/class_ninepatchrect.rst:14
msgid ""
"Scalable texture-based frame that tiles the texture's centers and sides, "
"but keeps the corners' original size. Perfect for panels and dialog "
"boxes."
msgstr "可伸缩的基于纹理的框架，可平铺纹理的中心和侧面，但保留角的原始大小。非常适合面板和对话框。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_ninepatchrect.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_ninepatchrect.rst:19
msgid ""
"Also known as 9-slice panels, NinePatchRect produces clean panels of any "
"size, based on a small texture. To do so, it splits the texture in a 3×3 "
"grid. When you scale the node, it tiles the texture's sides horizontally "
"or vertically, the center on both axes but it doesn't scale or tile the "
"corners."
msgstr ""
"``NinePatchRect`` "
"也称为9切片面板，它基于较小的纹理，生成任何大小的干净面板。为此，它将纹理分成3×3的网格。缩放节点时，它会水平或垂直地平铺纹理的边，两个轴的中心，但不会缩放或平铺角。"

